============================================
WEAPON TEMPLATE

[ExampleWeapon]
Type= What type of weapon is it?
Info= What you see when you use !view-info
Jobs= What job codes can use it? All is everyone, else WAR.PLD, etc
Rarity= 1-5, how rare is this item? 5 is considered Legendary
Stat= What primary stat is used to calculate damage done with this weapon?
Element= What element is this weapon?
WeaponLevel= What level is the weapon considered?
PlayerLevel= What level does the player need to be to use it?
Damage= Base damage with the weapon
Speed= Weapon speed (used to help determine init)

str=
dex=
vit=
int=
mnd=
pie=
det=
pdefense=
mdefense=

The above block of stats is used for if the weapon gives a bonus to any stat
upon equipping.

